snippet.title: Manor Lords - Gameplay Overview | Medieval RTS/Citybuilder
snippet.description:
Manor Lords is an upcoming strategy game for PC that combines deep, organic and realistic city building with large scale, tactical battles. 

Wishlist the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1363080/Manor_Lords/

This video showcases regional development, trade and recruitment. Next one will probably discuss the combat aspects of the game. 

The game is a work in progress and is subject to change.

Listen to the music track here:
https://youtu.be/NP1hZhtL9Aw

Patreon:
https://www.patreon.com/GregStyczen

Follow the game to learn more:
Website: https://manorlords.com/
Discord: https://discord.gg/RRD55RZdB7
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/manorlords_game/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/LordsManor
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/ManorLords/
